data.description: Take a step back in time with this beautiful 19th Century Historical home. It features original wood floors and millwork throughout. The living room has a beautiful stone gas fireplace with built in bookshelves, and a den/office area.  There are many updates on this home. It has a new roof, new electrical, new gutter leaf guards, new windows, new solar panels, new light fixtures, new furnace, and more. There is a security alarm. Featuring 4 spacious bedrooms, 1 full bath on the main floor and 1 full bath upstairs. The lot size is nearly half an acre, and has potential for a pool and can be beautifully landscaped. Enjoy the wrap- around covered back porch. The seller started to renovate the main bathroom shower and floor, and decided to let the new homeowners finish it. THE SELLER IS MOTIVATED, MUST SEE!  The seller is offering to leave the new bathroom, laundry, and kitchen flooring for you to finish if interested.
